@@ -882,7 +882,13 @@ EOF
 	then
 	    echo ${UNAME_MACHINE}-unknown-linux-gnu
 	else
-	    echo ${UNAME_MACHINE}-unknown-linux-gnueabi
+	    if echo __ARM_PCS_VFP | $CC_FOR_BUILD -E - 2>/dev/null \
+		| grep -q __ARM_PCS_VFP
+	    then
+		echo ${UNAME_MACHINE}-unknown-linux-gnueabi
+	    else
+		echo ${UNAME_MACHINE}-unknown-linux-gnueabihf
+	    fi
 	fi
 	exit ;;
     avr32*:Linux:*:*)
@@ -972,7 +978,7 @@ EOF
 	echo ${UNAME_MACHINE}-unknown-linux-gnu
 	exit ;;
